728877f-b.title: Richmond: Giffords Lane - Dewey Avenue
728877f-b.text:
137 Giffords Lane, adjoining the N.E. corner of Dcwey Avenue.
Mr. P.L. Sperr states that in this house were fommerly held
Catholic services and that the spring in the basement is said to
have been blessed by the priest for holy water.
June 13, 1927.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A view of the rear of the house, looking south.
June 13, 1927.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
